lutions%20to%20daily%20problems.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20summer%20before%20my%20senior%20year%20of%20college%2C%20while%20participating%20in%20a%20four-week%20intensive%20entrepreneurship%20program%2C%20Netflix%20cofounder%20Marc%20Randolph%20came%20to%20speak%20to%20my%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%2013%20years%20later%2C%20I%20still%20remember%20his%20advice%3A%20Build%20a%20product%20that%20solves%20a%20problem.%20He%20encouraged%20us%20to%20think%20about%20pain%20points%20in%20our%20own%20lives%20and%20how%20we%20could%20deliver%20a%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20my%20capstone%20project%20that%20summer%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20solve%20a%20problem%20I%20encountered%20nearly%20every%20day%20when%20I%20stepped%20onto%20a%20tennis%20court%3A%20After%20wearing%20out%20a%20handful%20of%20tennis%20balls%2C%20I'd%20toss%20them%20in%20the%20trash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20never%20followed%20through%20on%20my%20idea%20of%20upcycling%20dead%20tennis%20balls%20%E2%80%94%20turning%20them%20into%20outsoles%20or%20playground%20surfacing%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20general%20advice%20stuck.%20And%20as%20I've%20written%20about%20successful%20entrepreneurs%20over%20the%20years%2C%20I've%20noticed%20that%20many%20of%20them%20do%20exactly%20what%20Randolph%20instructed%20my%20class%20to%20do%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%20Garrett%20Gosselin%2C%20who%20became%20obsessed%20with%20pickleball%20when%20COVID%20hit%20and%20stripped%20him%20of%20his%20sommelier%20job.%20He%20started%20playing%20nearly%20every%20day%20of%20the%20week%20and%20competing%20in%20tournaments%20around%20Southern%20California%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he%20found%20himself%20cycling%20through%20a%20lot%20of%20paddles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20that%20time%2C%20they%20were%20all%20made%20out%20of%20fiberglass%2C%20and%20they%20all%20had%20really%20loud%2C%20vibrant%20graphics.%20They%20kind%20of%20looked%20like%20toys%2C%20and%20they%20were%20falling%20apart%20really%20fast%2C%26quot%3B%20Gosselin%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20need%20for%20a%20better%20paddle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22kyle%20goguen%20and%20garrett%20Gosselin%20-%20CRBN%20Pickleball%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689619e2cfc04e97619b1a4f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221095%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECRBN%20Pickleball%20cofounders%20and%20childhood%20friends%2C%20Kyle%20Goguen%20and%20Garrett%20Gosselin.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20CRBN%20Pickleball%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20decided%20to%20build%20his%20own%20%E2%80%94%20a%20sleek%20and%20durable%2C%20high-performance%20paddle%20with%20a%20carbon%20fiber%20face%20%E2%80%94%20he%20didn't%20intend%20to%20start%20a%20company.%20He%20simply%20wanted%20a%20better%20option%20for%20him%20and%20his%20doubles%20partner%20to%20use%20in%20competition.%20It%20wasn't%20until%20other%20people%20started%20noticing%20his%20prototype%20and%20asking%20where%20they%20could%20buy%20one%20that%20he%20ordered%20500%20units%20and%20set%20up%20a%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGosselin%20sold%20out%20within%20a%20week%20and%20couldn't%20keep%20his%20paddle%20in%20stock%20for%20the%20first%20two%20years%20of%20the%20business.%20The%20former%20somm%20now%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrbn-pickleball-paddles-former-sommelier-built-booming-ecommerce-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eruns%20CRBN%20full-time%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20manages%20a%20team%20of%2025%20employees%2C%20and%20has%20expanded%20to%20offering%20bags%2C%20eyewear%2C%20and%20apparel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20Gosselin%2C%20Jack%20Schrupp%20encountered%20a%20problem%20he%20decided%20to%20tackle%20first%20and%20foremost%20for%20himself.%20Schrupp%2C%20a%20former%20collegiate%20athlete%2C%20couldn't%20find%20a%20protein%20powder%20that%20suited%20his%20sensitive%20stomach.%20He%20bought%20a%20spice%20grinder%20and%20a%20small%20b