2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20cat%20doors%20she%20manufactured%20and%20listed%20online%20were%20profitable%20but%20not%20a%20smash%20hit.%20It%20was%20when%20she%20noticed%20a%20recurring%20customer%20comment%20%E2%80%94%20people%20wanted%20a%20closable%20door%2C%20rather%20than%20a%20cat%20door%20with%20flaps%20%E2%80%94%20that%20things%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpurrfectportal.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPurrfect%20Portal%3C%2Fa%3E%20started%20to%20take%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20solution%20to%20her%20customer%20requests%20was%20born%20out%20of%20a%20happy%20hour%20with%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomeone%20said%2C%20'What%20about%20a%20miniature%20door%3F%20A%20little%20human%20door%20with%20a%20little%20doorknob%20and%20a%20little%20window%20and%20a%20little%20door%20knocker%2C'%26quot%3B%20recalled%20Harrington.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20everyone%20just%20lost%20their%20minds%2C%20even%20the%20non-cat%20people.%20And%20in%20my%20gut%2C%20I%20knew%20people%20would%20love%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22lisa%20harrington%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688020c5f748d8c055f61891%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELisa%20Harrington%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20Purrfect%20Portal.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lisa%20Harrington%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20about%20two%20years%20to%20bring%20the%20happy%20hour%20vision%20to%20life%2C%20but%20when%20it%20launched%20in%202020%2C%20%26quot%3Bpeople%20just%20lost%20their%20minds%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20catapulted%20to%20the%20top%20of%20the%20bestseller%20list%20pretty%20quickly.%20We%20were%20selling%20100%20units%20a%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20once%20you%20identify%20a%20problem%20in%20your%20life%2C%20the%20next%20step%20is%20to%20solve%20it%20effectively%20%E2%80%94%20if%20you%20want%20to%20pursue%20the%20path%20of%20an%20entrepreneur%2C%20that%20is%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20takes%20a%20certain%20type%20of%20person%20to%20follow%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGosselin's%20childhood%20friend%20and%20business%20partner%20at%20CRBN%2C%20Kyle%20Goguen%2C%20gave%20insight%20into%20how%20Gosselin%20thinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20remember%20Garrett%20would%20brew%20his%20own%20kombucha%20and%20make%20his%20own%20sourdough%2C%20and%20he%20has%20always%20been%20this%20sort%20of%20inventor%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Goguen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20came%20to%20bringing%20the%20pickleball%20paddle%20he%20wanted%20to%20life%2C%20%26quot%3Bhe%20didn't%20have%20these%20barriers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20most%20people%20would%20be%20like%2C%20'How%20do%20I%20create%20a%20product%3F'%20Instead%2C%20he%20was%20just%20like%2C%20'I'm%20going%20to%20go%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20make%20it%20better%20because%20these%20problems%20exist.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-start-a-business-according-to-successful-entrepreneurs-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757755802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68c44ec6183847aa39d6ae53%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-start-a-business-according-to-successful-entrepreneurs-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three%20successful%20entrepreneurs%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20came%20up%20with%20their%20product%20ideas%20by%20solving%20a%20problem%20they%20faced%20in%20their%20own%20lives.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kelkins%40businessinsider.com%20(Kathleen%20Elkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-start-a-business-according-to-successful-entrepreneurs-2025-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22D