f%20no%20more%20than%20800%20yards%20could%20expand%20that%20to%2012%20miles%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-drones-volunteer-sternenko-donations-fpv-pilots-win-russia-war-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eflying%20the%20FPVs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20are%20controlled%20by%20an%20operator%20wearing%20virtual-reality%20goggles%20who%20can%20see%20the%20target%20from%20the%20drone's%20camera.%20These%20are%20the%20drones%20that%20have%20been%20deployed%20so%20lethally%20by%20Ukrainians%20on%20the%20front%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20changes%20are%20only%20beginning%20to%20take%20place.%20In%20a%20statement%20to%20POLITICO%2C%20Cuomo%20said%20his%20command%20at%20Quantico%2C%20Va.%20%E2%80%94%20where%20the%20Marine%20Corps%20develops%20its%20combat%20strategy%20%E2%80%94%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Blaser-focused%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20last%20two%20months%20on%20producing%20a%20training%20pamphlet%20that%20will%20teach%20%26quot%3Bhigh-volume%2C%20attritable%20drone%20employment.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20those%20training%20%26quot%3Bconcepts%26quot%3B%20will%20%26quot%3Bgo%20into%20effect%20across%20the%20Service%20beginning%20in%20September.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Marine%20with%20the%20Corps'%20Attack%20Drone%20Team%20controlled%20an%20aerial%20vehicle%20during%20an%20August%20demonstration%20in%20Quantico%2C%20Va.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68c1b7edf9db348adc0b3808%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221337%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Marine%20with%20the%20Corps'%20Attack%20Drone%20Team%20controlled%20an%20aerial%20vehicle%20during%20an%20August%20demonstration%20in%20Quantico%2C%20Va.%3Cp%3EConnor%20Taggart%2FUS%20Marine%20Corps%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Navy%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20working%20on%20long-term%20plans%20to%20use%20swarms%20of%20drones%20to%20turn%20the%20Taiwan%20Strait%