22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAngel%20Studios%20CEO%20Neal%20Harmon%20(center%20left)%20rang%20the%20bell%20at%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange%20on%20Thursday.%3Cp%3EAngel%20Studios%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAngel%20Studios%2C%20the%20company%20behind%20the%20surprise%20blockbuster%20%26quot%3BSound%20of%20Freedom%2C%26quot%3B%20just%20went%20public.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhile%20the%20studio%20is%20known%20for%20its%20faith-based%20programming%2C%20its%20green-lighting%20model%20sets%20it%20apart.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAngel's%20leadership%20team%20shared%20the%20pitch%20they're%20giving%20investors.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAngel%20Studios%20just%20went%20public%20and%20is%20selling%20investors%20on%20a%20business%20model%20that%20gives%20its%20streaming%20subscribers%20creative%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Utah-based%20studio%20is%20known%20for%20its%20faith-themed%20and%20%26quot%3Bvalues-driven%26quot%3B%20movies%20and%20TV%20shows%2C%20like%20making%20the%202023's%20sleeper%20box-office%20hit%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsound-of-freedom-deemed-box-office-hit-liberals-have-doubts-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BSound%20of%20Freedom%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20its%20involvement%20in%20the%20%26quot%3BThe%20Chosen%26quot%3B%20series%20based%20on%20the%20life%20of%20Jesus%20Christ.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAngel's%20name%20isn't%20only%20about%20religion.%20It's%20also%20a%20nod%20to%20its%20unconventional%20green-lighting%20process.%20Angel's%20streaming%20subscribers%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0with%20plans%20starting%20at%20%2412%20a%20month%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0double%20as%20%26quot%3Bangel%20investors%26quot%3B%20who%20can%20vote%20on%20what%20future%20films%20get%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20problem%20isn't%20with%20what's%20being%20made%2C%26quot%3B%20Angel%20CEO%20Neal%20Harmon%20said%20of%20Hollywood.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20with%20what's%20not%20being%20made.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarmon%20founded%20the%20company%20alongside%20three%20of%20his%20eight%20siblings%20%E2%80%94%20Jeffrey%2C%20Jordan%2C%20and%20Daniel%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20cousin.%20Neal%2C%20Jeffrey%2C%20and%20Jordan%20spoke%20with%20Business%20Insider%20about%20what%20sets%20their%20studio%20apart%2C%20hours%20after%20Angel's%20stock%20debuted%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAngel%20went%20public%20through%20a%20merger%20with%20a%20special%20purpose%20acquisition%20company%20(SPAC)%20called%20Southport%20Acquisition%20Corporation.%20Its%20stock%2C%20which%20trades%20under%20the%20ticker%20ANGX%2C%20has%20been%20volatile%20since%20its%20debut%2C%20swinging%20between%20%2410.35%20and%20%2420.39.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20generated%20%24135%20million%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%202025%2C%20with%20a%20net%20loss%20of%20%2453.3%20million%20in%20that%20span.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brothers%2C%20who%20repeatedly%20called%20themselves%20%26quot%3BIdaho%20farm%20boys%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20interview%2C%20are%20proud%20to%20be%20Hollywood%20outsiders.%20They%20believe%20they've%20found%20a%20lucrative%20niche%20in%20what%20they're%20making%20and%20how%20they're%20making%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222b454bc0-5b2e-4352-baa9-0555b0ec963c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%20there%20be%20green%20lights%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAngel's%20mission%20statement%20is%20to%20%26quot%3Bamplify%20light%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20a%20deliberately%20ambiguous%20motto%20that%20%26quot%3Bmeans%20different%20things%20to%20different%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jeffrey%2C%20Angel's%20content%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%201.5%20million%20members%20in%20the%20so-called%20Angel%20Guild%20want%20their%20faith%20represented%2C%20while%20others%20yearn%20for%20wholesome%2C%20family-friendly%20shows%2C%20Jeffrey%20said.%20Angel%20Guild%20members%20can%20vote%20on%20what%20projects%20get%20made%2C%20and%20can%20even%20give%20direct%20feedback%20to%20the%20production%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20making%20movies%20that%20its%20fans%20have%20already%20endorsed%2C%20Angel%20Studios'%20films%20tend%20to%20generate%20strong%20audience%20scores%20on%20sites%20like%20Rotten%20Tomatoes%20%E2%80%94%20and%20robust%20ticket%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAngel%20Studios%20earned%20an%20average%20of%20%2434.7%20million%20per%20movie%20released%20from%202023%20to%202025%2C%20which%20is%20higher%20than%20any%20other%20independent%20studio%2C%20according%20to%20media%20analyst%20Evan%20Shapiro.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndustry%20analysts%20say%20this%20fan-centered%20approach%20has%20shown%20promise%20so%20far%20and%20could%20have%20staying%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAngel%20%26quot%3Bspecializes%20in%20mobilizing%20underserved%20audiences%26quot%3B%20with%20its%20inexpensive%2C%20faith-centered%20content%2C%20said%20Brandon%20Katz%20of%20entertainment%20data%20provider%20Greenlight%20Analytics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%20specific%20audience%20hungry%20for%20programming%20that%20appeals%20to%20their%20particular%20tastes%20and%20values%2C%26quot%3B%20Katz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKPMG%20media%20analyst%20Frank%20Albarella%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Btoday's%20audiences%20are%20rejecting%20one-size-fits-all%20content%20creation%20in%20favor%20of%20platforms%20that%20turn%20viewers%20into%20creative%20collaborators.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228a76a2d7-fbf3-42fc-acf4-27070674b411%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPay%20models%20and%20'growing%20pains'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAngel%20is%20also%20pitching%20a%20distinct%20pay%20model%20for%20creators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20upended%20the%20entertainment%20business%20over%20a%20decade%20ago%20with%20a%20cost-plus%20model%20that%20paid%20filmmakers%20as%20if%20their%20movie%20was%20a%20modest%20hit.%20While%20this%20reduces%20risks%2C%20it%20also%20caps%20creatives'%20upside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20overpays%20for%20failures%20and%20it%20underpays%20for%20success%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jordan%2C%20who's%20Angel's%20president.%20Angel's%20model%20shares%20half%20of%20the%20profits%20from%20a%20title%20with%20its%20creator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAngel%20has%20had%20some%20business%20%26quot%3Bgrowing%20pains%2C%26quot%3B%20Jordan%20said.%20Two%20production%20companies%20that%20partnered%20with%20Angel%20have%20since%20terminated%20their%20arrangements%2C%20leading%20to%20legal%20fights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDallas%20Jenkins%2C%20creator%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Chosen%2C%26quot%3B%20accused%20Angel%20of%20contract%20violations.%20Arbitrators%20ruled%20in%20Jenkins'%20favor%2C%20officially%20severing%20his%20business%20relationship%20with%20the%20company.%20Angel%20has%20appealed%20the%20decision.%20Slingshot%2C%20which%20made%20the%20%26quot%3BDavid%26quot%3B%20animated%20movie%20based%20on%20the%20biblical%20character%2C%20terminated%20its%20deal.%20Angel%20responded%20with%20a%20lawsuit%2C%20which%20is%20ongoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLawsuits%20in%20the%20entertainment%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20like%20pigeons%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%26quot%3B%20Jordan%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20the%20reality%20of%20this%20space.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Harmon%20brothers%20first%20learned%20that%20when%20launching%20VidAngel%2C%20which%20removed%20profanity%20and%20sexual%20content%20from%20movies.%20Disney%20sued%20in%20response%2C%20and%20the%20subsequent%20ruling%20pushed%20VidAngel%20into%20bankruptcy.%20A%20few%20years%20later%2C%20the%20Harmons%20rebounded%20by%20starting%20Angel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20years%20since%2C%20Angel%20has%20turned%20heads%20in%20Hollywood%20through%20its%20unique%20relationship%20with%20its%20streaming%20subscribers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJeffrey%20said%20that%20being%20a%20publicly%20traded%20company%20is%20an%20extension%20of%20that%20mission%2C%20describing%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20ultimate%20grassroots.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busine