sinsider.com%2Fdisney-world-jobs-recruiter-interview-application-advice-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estarted%20at%20Disney%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202011%20with%20an%20eight-month%20internship%20as%20a%20cast%20member.%20My%20end%20goal%20was%20to%20go%20back%20after%20finishing%20my%20degree%20and%20rise%20through%20the%20company's%20ranks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20young%2C%20my%20parents%20took%20me%20to%20Disneyland.%20I%20was%20wearing%20a%20pair%20of%20Mickey%20ears%2C%20and%20I%20remember%20seeing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmickey-mouse-from-1928-steamboat-willie-now-in-public-domain-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMickey%20Mouse%3C%2Fa%3E%20go%20by%20on%20his%20train%20float.%20He%20pointed%20at%20me%2C%20then%20at%20his%20own%20ears%2C%20and%20then%20back%20to%20my%20ears.%20It%20became%20a%20core%20memory%2C%20so%20for%20the%20longest%20time%2C%20I%20felt%20a%20strong%20personal%20connection%20to%20the%20Disney%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20dedicated%20to%20Disney%2C%20and%20I%20rose%20through%20the%20ranks%20into%20a%20senior%20manager%20position%20in%20an%20HR-type%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20I%20got%20furloughed%20when%20the%20park%20closed%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20and%20I%20decided%20to%20fill%20my%20time%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-full-time-job-fiverr-freelance-side-hustle-business-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efreelancing%20for%20fun%20on%20Fiverr%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20a%20year%2C%20my%20earnings%20on%20Fiverr%20began%20exceeding%20what%20I%20made%20monthly%20at%20Disney.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20left%20Disney%2C%20my%20salary%20was%20over%20%2460%2C000.%20So%20far%20in%202025%2C%20I've%20made%20a%20net%20of%20over%20%24100%2C000%2C%20and%20overall%2C%20I've%20made%20more%20than%20%24900%2C000%20on%20Fiverr%20since%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3EDid%20you%20quit%20your%20job%20or%20pivot%20to%20freelancing%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20to%20share%20your%20story%20at%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Amhoff%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emhoff%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226d84a3cf-cca4-4198-974d-d1c0bf987297%5C%22%3EI%20was%20furloughed%20from%20Disney%20in%202020%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-college-program-interview-careers-tips-advice-disney-world-job-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAt%20Disney%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20were%20many%20options%20we%20could%20pivot%20into%20internally.%20My%20final%20role%20was%20an%20operations-based%20role%2C%20focused%20on%20employee%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20did%20onboarding%2C%20training%2C%20and%20partnering%20with%20recruiters%20to%20make%20sure%20we%20were%20getting%20people%20into%20the%20right%20spaces.%20That%20became%20a%20passion%20of%20mine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20I%20was%20furloughed%2C%20I%20signed%20up%20for%20a%20Fiverr%20account%20in%20May%202020.%20I%20posted%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbecame-multimillionaire-writing-resumes-work-life-balance-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egig%20for%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20writing%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20I%20thought%20that%20was%20likely%20the%20closest%20thing%20to%20HR%20that%20I%20could%20do%20on%20that%20platform%2C%20and%20it%20played%20to%20my%20writing%20strengths.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20got%20my%20first%20order%20with%20Fiverr%20that%20summer%2C%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%3Cem%3EOh%2C%20no%2C%20what%20am%20I%20supposed%20to%20do%3F%20Some%20random%20person%20on%20the%20internet%20found%20a%20stranger%20%E2%80%94%20me%20and%20my%20profile%20%E2%80%94%20and%20trusts%20me%20to%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecruiter-who-has-written-over-700-resumes-best-advice-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22