Office%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20watchdog%20agency%20that%20reports%20to%20Congress%2C%20the%20Air%20Force%20believes%20it%20must%20continue%20to%20maintain%20Minuteman%20III%20missiles%20over%20the%20next%20decade%20and%20beyond%20while%20Sentinel%20is%20completed.%20Sentinel%2C%20manufactured%20by%20Northrop%20Grumman%2C%20was%20originally%20planned%20to%20replace%20all%20450%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-air-force-aborts-planned-test-launch-of-icbm-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMinuteman%20III%20missiles%3C%2Fa%3E%20beginning%20later%20this%20decade%20at%20an%20estimated%20cost%20of%20%2478%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20years%20since%20the%20Sentinel%20contract%20was%20awarded%20in%202020%2C%20both%20the%20delivery%20timeline%20and%20cost%20have%20ballooned.%20The%20US%20Department%20of%20Defense%20estimates%20the%20Sentinel%20will%20now%20cost%20over%20%24140%20billion%20and%20be%20delayed%20by%20years%2C%20with%20deployment%20potentially%20expected%20sometime%20in%20the%202030s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225199%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20US%20Air%20Force%20Airmen%20work%20on%20maintenance%20within%20a%20missile%20silo.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68c44de457d362d375e81206%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223714%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWork%20to%20keep%20Minuteman%20III%20operational%20will%20be%20significant%20in%20the%20coming%20decades.%3Cp%3EUS%20Air%20Force%20photo%20by%20Staff%20Sgt.%20Michael%20A.%20Richmond%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pentagon%20has%20blamed%20this%20on%20an%20unrealistic%20delivery%20schedule%2C%20problems%20with%20Sentinel's%20engineering%20and%20system%20design%2C%20an%20atrophied%20ICBM%20industrial%20base%2C%20and%20organizational%20issues%20within%20the%20Air%20Force%2C%20GAO%20said.%20ICBMs%20are%20the%20land-based%20element%20of%20the%20US'%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-showed-full-nuclear-triad-world-first-time-military-parade-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enuclear%20triad%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20also%20includes%20submarine-launched%20ballistic%20missiles%20and%20nuclear%20bombs%20carried%20by%20aircraft%20like%20the%20B-2%20bomber.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Sentinel%20is%20a%20three-stage%20solid-fuel%20missile%20that%20will%20purportedly%20have%20a%20lighter%20carbon%20composite%20structure%20and%20more%20advanced%20electronics%20and%20systems%20for%20easier%20upgrades.%20It's%20also%20expected%20to%20be%20able%20to%20carry%20more%20warheads%20than%20its%20predecessor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Air%20Force%20has%20said%20transitioning%20from%20Minuteman%20III%20to%20Sentinel%20is%20a%20complex%20project%20involving%20not%20only%20converting%20old%20silos%20to%20new%20ones%20capable%20of%20hosting%20Sentinel%20but%20also%20keeping%20Minuteman%20III%20forces%20in%20a%20ready%20status%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewhile%20Sentinel%20is%20introduced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20Lt.%20Gen.%20Andrew%20Gebara%2C%20the%20Air%20Force's%20deputy%20chief%20of%20staff%20for%20strategic%20deterrence%20and%20nuclear%20integration%2C%20said%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mitchellaerospacepower.org%2Fevents%2Flt-gen-andrew-gebara-an%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMitchell%20Institute%20for%20Aerospace%20Studies%3C%2Fa%3E%20think%20tank%20event%20that%20cost%20growth%20was%20largely%20attributed%20to%20infrastructure%20work%20to%20build%20%26quot%3Ball%20the%20launch%20facilities%2C%20all%20the%20launch%20centers%2C%20all%20the%20wiring%2C%20all%20that%20goes%20into%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20larger%20critical%20missteps%20in%20the%20Air%20Force's%20management%20of%20Sentinel%20and%20the%20transition%20to%20the%20new%20ICBM%20have%20been%20documented%20for%20years.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffas.org%2Fpublication%2Fthe-two-hundred-billion-dollar-boondoggle%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFederation%20of%20American%20Scientists%3C%2Fa%3E%20think%20tank%20wrote%20that%20the%20Air%20Force%20%26quot%3Bassumed%20that%20the%20Sentinel%20would%20be%20able%20to%20reuse%20much%20of%20the%20original%20Minuteman%20launch%20infrastructure%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20refurbishment%20of%20450%20missile%20silos.%20Now%2C%20it%20appears%20the%20service%20will%20have%20to%20build%20new%20launch%20facilities%2C%20including%20new%20silos%20%E2%80%94%20hardened%20underground%20launchers%20spread%20across%20the%20central%20US%20where%20the%20missiles%20are%20maintained%20and%20kept%20in%20a%20high%20state%20of%20readiness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224090%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Air%20Force%20Global%20Strike%20Command%20Minuteman%20III%20ICBM%20test-fired%20Tuesday%20from%20Vandenberg%20Air%20Force%20Base%2C%20California.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62fbcd64c87abe0018c2bccb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222922%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Air%20Force%20Global%20Strike%20Command%20Minuteman%20III%20ICBM%20test-fired%20Tuesday%20from%20Vandenberg%20Air%20Force%20Base%2C%20California.%3Cp%3EUS%20Air%20Force%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20the%20Air%20Force%20will%20continue%20to%20operate%20and%20maintain%20its%20Minuteman%20III%20system%20as%20a%20nuclear%20deterrent%2C%20with%20the%20timeline%20to%20retire%20them%20still%20being%20figured%20out%20by%20the%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20keeping%20Minuteman%20III%20missiles%20online%20will%20be%20challenging.%20Per%20the%20report%2C%20many%20parts%20for%20the%20ICBM%20are%20either%20limited%20in%20supply%20or%20obsolete%2C%20and%20the%20Air%20Force%20doesn't%20have%20a%20plan%20for%20continued%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-carried-out-back-to-back-icbm-launches-minuteman-iii-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMinuteman%20